high_descs: Turn right and head into the kitchen, turning right again to go to the countertop.
Remove the knife from the microwave.
Exit the kitchen area the way you came in and go straight ahead to the far end of the couch on the left.
Slice the head of lettuce sitting on the couch.
Go to the other end of the sofa.
Place the knife down on the sofa.
Return to the sofa with the sliced lettuce.
Pick up the lettuce from the couch.
Return to the kitchen area and go to the fridge in the corner.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and head back to the couch, stopping at the diningtable in front of it.
Place the lettuce on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled piece of Lettuce on a DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to a countertop and then right again to a microwave.
Take the knife out of the microwave.
Go back to where you came from, continue straight until you reach the lettuce, then go left to a tall lamp, and turn left at the sofa.
Cut the lettuce on the sofa with the knife.
Go to the other side of the sofa, walking around the oval table.
Place the knife on the sofa.
Go back to the sofa where you left the cut bread.
Pick up a lettuce from the sofa.
Now go across the room to the fridge.
Put the lettuce inside the fridge, let it cool for a bit, and take it out.
Now go back to the oval diningtable next to sofa.
Put the lettuce on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled lettuce on the diningtable

go to the microwave, open the knife.

walk back to the other side of the lettuce.

anns.task_desc: Get slice of lettuce to the diningtable
